Description: Timebomb - Auto-delete files/folders after a chosen duration via right-click menu
 A utility for Ubuntu/Linux (GNOME/Nautilus) to schedule automatic deletion of files and folders via right-click menu. Includes timer scripts, cleaner, and systemd integration.
